{"nodes": [{"id": "docs_demo_overview", "label": "Kanban Agents Demo (demo.gif)", "file_type": "image", "source_file": "docs/demo.gif", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "52s screen recording walkthrough of the kanban-agents product. Numbered overlay narrates 6 steps: (1) carte creation, (2) ticket detail, (3) feasibility analysis, (5) Claude implements autonomously, (6) automatic review/tests/PR, ending on 'PR #142 ouverte'. Tagline: 'Du ticket a la pull request, sans quitter le tableau.'"}, {"id": "docs_demo_kanban_board", "label": "Kanban Board (Atelier)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/demo.gif", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Desktop app 'Atelier' with sidebar (Home, Terminals, Stats) and top tabs (Kanban, Agents, Workflow, Worktree). Columns: TODO, A implementer, PRD, A review, Fini. Cards carry project labels (kanban-agents, atelier-web) and a worktree-slots indicator ('4 disponibles, 1 utilises')."}, {"id": "docs_demo_ticket_creation", "label": "New Ticket Modal", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/demo.gif", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "'Nouveau ticket' modal with tabs Nouveau ticket / Import CSV / PR Review / PR Cleaner / Ask / Worktree. Fields: Titre, Projet, Lien externe, Branche de base du worktree, Description markdown, Depend du ticket (stack PR). Actions: Annuler, Creer, Creer et lancer."}, {"id": "docs_demo_agent_config", "label": "Agent Implementation Config", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/demo.gif", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Per-ticket config: model choice Opus / Sonnet / Haiku, effort level (high), and toggles PRD, PR draft, Auto-merge, Argus multi-loop, Screenshots."}, {"id": "docs_demo_ticket_detail", "label": "Ticket Detail View", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/demo.gif", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Modal with DESCRIPTION / ACTIVITE tabs and DETAILS panel (Branche feat/cost-on-card, Base main, Modele opus-high, Implementeur Claude Code, Faisabilite). Embeds an agent Terminal that appears once the ticket runs in 'A implementer'."}, {"id": "docs_demo_feasibility_analysis", "label": "Feasibility Analysis", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/demo.gif", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "'Analyser la faisabilite' action sets the Faisabilite field from '-' to 'Implementable' before implementation begins (step 3 of the demo)."}, {"id": "docs_demo_claude_code_agent", "label": "Claude Code Autonomous Agent", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/demo.gif", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Agent session ('Claude Code - session ticket-a3f9 - slot-2') runs in the embedded terminal, explores code (Read TicketCard.tsx, Grep 'TicketCost'), edits files, and drives the work to completion autonomously (step 5)."}, {"id": "docs_demo_contract", "label": "Ticket Contract Injection", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/demo.gif", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Terminal logs 'Contrat recu - ticket #142 (kind: feature)' showing the ticket spec is injected into the agent session as a contract before work starts."}, {"id": "docs_demo_stage_machine", "label": "Stage State Machine", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/demo.gif", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Agent emits explicit stage transitions: update_stage -> implementing -> reviewing -> testing -> opening_pr, terminating with done(pr_url). Each transition gates the next action."}, {"id": "docs_demo_argus_review", "label": "Argus Code Review", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/demo.gif", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "On the reviewing stage the agent 'Lance argus (revue de code en sous-agents)' producing '0 bug bloquant, 1 nit corrige' before tests run."}, {"id": "docs_demo_automated_tests", "label": "Automated Tests (typecheck/lint/test)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/demo.gif", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "On the testing stage the agent runs 'bun run typecheck', 'bun run lint', 'bun test' (all passing) as an automated quality gate."}, {"id": "docs_demo_pull_request", "label": "Automated Pull Request", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/demo.gif", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "opening_pr stage pushes 'git push -u origin feat/cost-on-card' and ends with 'done(pr_url) -> PR #142 ouverte'. Closing card celebrates 'PR #142 ouverte'."}, {"id": "docs_demo_worktree_slots", "label": "Worktree Slots", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/demo.gif", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Board header shows 'Slots: 4 disponibles, 1 utilises'; the agent session is bound to 'slot-2'. Each running ticket occupies a worktree slot for parallel isolated execution."}, {"id": "docs_demo_workflow_pipeline", "label": "Ticket-to-PR Pipeline", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/demo.gif", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Final overlay diagram: P